Title: Winter's End
Plot: After April collapses and goes into early labor, Jake makes Kenchy face his problems so that they can save April. The wind turbine arrives from New Bern but Heather does not return. Jericho makes a deal with New Bern to send ten of their people to New Bern to make more wind turbines as long as New Bern receives a percentage of their spring crop.
GuestStars: Timothy Omundson, Erica Tazel, David Meunier, Janet Hoskins, Jerry Giles, Clare Carey, Darby Stanchfield, Aasif Mandvi, Ron Bottitta, Beau Dremann
